quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,UMvelinqangi usungula indalo bese eyiphinda bese nibuyiselwa kuyena
  30,12,Futhi ngosuku ekuyofika ngalo ihora izoni ziyopheleliswa ngethemba
  30,13,Futhi angeke babenabo abakhulumeli phakathi kwezithixo zabo futhi bayoziphika izithixo zabo
  30,14,"Futhi ngosuku ekuyofika ngalo ihora, ngalolosuku bayohlukaniswa"
  30,15,Ngakho-ke labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle ezilungileyo bayokuba sengadini yentokozo
  30,16,Futhi labo abangakholwanga abaphika amavesi ethu kanye nokuhlangana kwempilo ezayo labo bayolethwa esijezisweni
  30,17,Ngakho-ke udumo malube kuMvelinqangi ngenkathi ningena kusihlwa nangenkathi ningena ekuseni
  30,18,Futhi udumo lungolwakho emazulwini nasemhlabeni nasebusuku nasemini
  30,19,Uveza ophilayo kofileyo futhi uveza ofile kophilayo futhi uphilisa umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo futhi niyovezwa kanjalo